<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3858359>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Cervonema proberti sp. nov. A. Ƌ anterior body region. B. ♀ anterior region. C. ♀ tail. D. Sperm cells. E. Ƌ posterior body region, showing copulatory apparatus. Scale bar: A, B, and C = 25 μm; D = 20 μm; E = 35 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3858359/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3858361>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Cervonema proberti sp. nov. A. ♀ head, showing glands. B. Entire Ƌ. C. ♀ reproductive system. Arrows point to clear globular inclusions in intestine wall. Scale bar: A =20 μm; B and C = 65 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3858361/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

